{"tid":975193,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺新主場最快3月中啟用","createTime":"2019-01-09T12:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T19:48:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"20b0249e892e896d58e4c348b910b58838c3783c","tid":975193,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=KhbF78JRf%2B7lJ43POXUJH2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=45465b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】熱刺終收到新主場的進度報告，無奈最快要到3月中才能啟用，肯定錯過北倫敦打吡大戰。<br />\n<br />\n一拖再拖的熱刺新球場，終算收到好消息，承建商Mace已發出進度報告，預計能夠在2月進行2場測試賽。如無意外，熱刺最快可以在3月中正式搬入新球場，即使錯過了3月2日對仇家阿仙奴的大戰，但有望在3月16日對水晶宮時揭幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換言之，球隊在歐聯16強對多蒙特，也肯定留在溫布萊舉行。「我要再次向球迷道歉，也感謝大家的耐性。」熱刺主帥利維（Daniel Levy）承認原本打算於去年9月開幕，但一直延期到今年3月中，進度未如理想，但考慮到安全問題，也是無辦法中的辦法。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺新主場將可容納62062人，並會舉辦NFL的正式比賽。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"ce976c864400d321b2fbb5a468cda6ec3bead963","tid":975193,"uid":121058,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"獎杯陳列室幾時啟用"},{"pid":"3d87a2b4a9cbd9581c56cd12ba27e25858be63c1","tid":975193,"uid":204475,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"轉新擂台算啦，橫掂都係打mma<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9453411ee30af9cfaa1126e65c364eaafa189cb","tid":975193,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"屌 起個水立方好過啦，跳水比賽贏硬"},{"pid":"05ffc18fd46a4ffb4dbb51c64d506c414c528ead","tid":975193,"uid":171157,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f9453411ee30af9cfaa1126e65c364eaafa189cb","tid":975193,"uid":118973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"屌 起個水立方好過啦，跳水比賽贏硬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rijekasport.hr/sites/default/files/field/image/145a35f0-